findprop <- function(x) {
  value <- x[1]
  samples <- x[-1]
  prop <- length(samples[samples<value])/length(samples)
  prop
}

fbarhat <- function(yobs, ysample) {
  # yobs m by 1
  # ysample N by m

  x <- cbind(yobs, t(ysample))
  dim(x)
  y <- na.omit(x)
  dim(y)
  x <- y[, -1]
  dim(x)
  length(yk)
  N <- ncol(x)
  N
  # x is the matrix of MCMC  samples
  m <- nrow(x)
  amat <- matrix(NA, nrow=m, ncol=K)
  for (i in 1:m) {
    ynewmat <- matrix(x[i, ], nrow=N, ncol=K, byrow=TRUE)
    dim(yomat)
    u <- rbind(yk, ynewmat)
    dim(u)
    v <- apply(u, 2, findprop)
    amat[i, ] <- as.vector(v)
  }
  Fbarhat <- apply(amat, 2, mean)
  # dans <- Fbarhat - Ghat
  Fbarhat
}

findprop <- function(x) {
  value <- x[1]
  samples <- x[-1]
  prop <- length(samples[samples<value])/length(samples)
  prop
}

fbarhat <- function(yobs, ysample) {
  # yobs m by 1
  # ysample N by m

 x <- cbind(yobs, t(ysample))
 dim(x)
 y <- na.omit(x)
 dim(y)
 x <- y[, -1]
 dim(x)
 length(yk)
 N <- ncol(x)
 N
# x is the matrix of MCMC  samples
  m <- nrow(x)
  amat <- matrix(NA, nrow=m, ncol=K)
    for (i in 1:m) {
      ynewmat <- matrix(x[i, ], nrow=N, ncol=K, byrow=TRUE)
      dim(yomat)
      u <- rbind(yk, ynewmat)
      dim(u)
      v <- apply(u, 2, findprop)
      amat[i, ] <- as.vector(v)
    }
    Fbarhat <- apply(amat, 2, mean)
 # dans <- Fbarhat - Ghat
 Fbarhat
}
